metadata.title: SmartBones SmartSticks, Treat Your Dog to a Rawhide-Free Chew Made With Real Meat and Vegetables
features: RAWHIDE-FREE CHEWS SmartSticks chews are easy to digest and 100 percent delicious
REAL CHICKEN AND PEANUT BUTTER These rawhide-free stick chews are made with real chicken or peanut butter for a scrumptious taste your dog can’t resist
VITAMIN AND MINERAL ENRICHED These chews are a healthy alternative to rawhide and vitamin and mineral enriched
HELPS MAINTAIN HEALTHY TEETH Chewing helps maintain healthy teeth
QUANTITY Contains 12-count bag of chews your dog will love
description: SmartSticks chews have all the benefits of a rawhide chew without the rawhide No-rawhide SmartSticks chews are made with real chicken or peanut butter for a scrumptious taste dogs can’t resist SmartSticks brand is mixing it up by offering two of the top flavors pups love in one mouthwatering pack – chicken and peanut butter These SmartSticks chews are made with real chicken or peanut butter for a scrumptious taste your dog can’t resist A healthy alternative to rawhide these rawhide-free chews are easy to digest vitamin and mineral enriched and 100 percent delicious Chewing helps maintain healthy teeth Contains 12 stick chews your dog will love Feed your dog 1 to 2 chews per day Always supervise your pup during chewing activity These chews are for intermittent or supplemental feeding only Select a chew slightly larger than your pet’s mouth Store in a cool dry place After opening reseal or store in an airtight container to preserve freshness Always provide plenty of fresh drinking water and visit your veterinarian regularly.
